{
  "texts": [
    "Additional fingerprints were also used to characterize different aspects of drugs.",
    "These include side effect profiles [5], interaction profiles [6,7], and target profiles [8][9][10][11][12].",
    "Side effect profiles provide information about the observed adverse effects associated with drugs.",
    "Interaction profiles describe the partners involved in drug interactions and record the drugs with which a particular drug tends to interact.",
    "Finally, target profiles describe the biological targets with which drugs interact.Deep learning-based methods have shown great potential to improve the accuracy of DDI prediction by learning more informative and discriminative features directly from the raw molecular structures."
  ]
}